{"ts":"2026-07-13T08:58:16.372Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-p9sc"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-535: pm deps omits dangling parent references (missing_count:0, missing:false) contradicting validate's dangling_reference_count"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"When an item's parent points at a deleted/missing id, pm deps <child> reports node_count:1, missing_count:0, missing:false — a false clean view — while pm validate correctly reports dangling_reference_count:1. deps builds its tree only from resolvable nodes and drops unresolvable parent edges silently. Fix: include unresolvable parent/blocked_by/dep targets as missing nodes (missing:true, missing_count>=1) so deps and validate agree; the check-side classification from pm-ol5v (dependency_references) is the shared source of truth — reuse it rather than a second detector. Secondary observation from the issue: pm delete permits deleting a still-referenced parent without warning/reparenting — evaluate a referenced-parent guard or advisory at fix time (keep in this item unless it grows). Active/legacy split for validate noise stays owned by pm-2ler."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["cli","deps","gh-issue","governance"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-13T08:58:16.372Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T08:58:16.372Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":90},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"deps reports missing nodes for dangling parent/dep references consistent with validate; delete-referenced-parent advisory evaluated; regression tests incl. deleted-parent repro; GH-535 closed"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-33cw"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-2ler","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-13T08:58:16.372Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"16d807bf0d3b9bcabd5ca945f433e3aba3f6f11f4e09548cc492294e718be9b3","message":""}
